body: Read the latest Campaign catchup here, and sign up below to get the best of Australia’s 2016 election sent to you every afternoon.        If you’re reading this in the Guardian app, tap on ‘Australian election briefing’ at the top or bottom of this page, then tap on ‘Follow series’ to get an app notification as soon as the Campaign catchup publishes every afternoon. Or try our other emails:  The Guardian Today - Australia edition Australian Politics First Dog on the Moon Morning Mail Find them all here
webTitle: The Australian election stories you need to read, in one handy email
